Additional Terms for Research Use
----------------------------------

This project includes anonymized honeypot telemetry data ("Dataset") collected
during live research operations. The Dataset is made available under the
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

If you use the Dataset or methodology described in this repository in an
academic publication, please cite:

  Chakraborty, C. S. (2025). Deception-Based Threat Detection Using T-Pot
  Multi-Service Honeypot: Real-World Attacker TTP Analysis and Threat
  Intelligence Feed Generation. GitHub Repository.
  https://github.com/ChandraVerse/honeypot-threat-intelligence

All captured IP addresses included in public sample data have been partially
anonymized. The full unanonymized dataset is retained privately and is
available to verified researchers upon request.
